            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日11:06，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲91.99點（或1%），暫報9331.28點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+8.56%</li><li>近 1 月：+20.83%</li><li>近 3 月：+17.89%</li><li>近 6 月：+36.53%</li><li>今年以來：+30.44%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)領漲。安森美半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ON:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ON\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ON-US</a>)上漲9.72%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲6.53%；超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)上漲5.63%；安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)上漲5.14%；格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK